---
title: Middle Eastern Chickpea-Stuffed Capsicum with Leafy Couscous & Garlic Yoghurt
description: If you’re as crazy about capsicums as we are then gather around and try out the latest capsicum creation - they’re stuffedfull
of saucy cannellini beans and sprinkled in Cheddar cheese to add a melted gooey layer on top. We’re these stuffedcapsicum’s
number one fans!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
